20
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:11,030
-My goodness.
-Mom!

21
00:01:11,930 --> 00:01:13,370
Yi-chan.

22
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:17,170
No! Stay with me.

23
00:01:17,240 --> 00:01:19,010
Stay with me, sweetheart.

24
00:01:20,039 --> 00:01:22,980
My baby. Were you scared?

25
00:01:23,810 --> 00:01:26,350
It's okay now. Everything's okay.

26
00:01:26,510 --> 00:01:27,850
Let's go now.

27
00:02:27,310 --> 00:02:29,740
Oh, no. Where are my car keys?

28
00:02:30,380 --> 00:02:31,710
Yi-chan, there's a problem.

29
00:02:32,510 --> 00:02:33,720
My car keys...

30
00:02:35,050 --> 00:02:38,620
Gosh. Yi-chan, what do we do?

31
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:40,720
Hold on a second.

32
00:02:43,829 --> 00:02:46,360
Excuse me! Help!

33
00:02:58,640 --> 00:03:01,480
Goodness. What happened? Are you okay?

34
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:02,680
Yes.

35
00:03:13,350 --> 00:03:18,760
[An Unfamiliar Place, a New Friend]

36
00:03:27,870 --> 00:03:29,870
I'm so sorry about this.

37
00:03:30,370 --> 00:03:32,340
I can't believe I even lost my car keys.

38
00:03:32,910 --> 00:03:34,210
Not a problem.

39
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:36,950
It's okay, so don't worry too much.

40
